The paper discusses the interaction between humans and AI systems in high-stakes domains, which is a topic that falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also focuses on the performance of AI systems, which is a core topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the potential risks associated with updates to AI systems, which is a topic that falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CYBER). Finally, the paper proposes methods for improving the compatibility of AI updates with prior user experience, which is a topic that falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HCI).
